subject: Football
College Athletics
organizations: Rutgers, The State University of New Jersey
lead_paragraph: Suddenly the tristate area has a college football powerhouse. On the surface, it seems like a nice thing. Below the surface, it is as if someone opened a bait-and-tackle shop next door to Bergdorf’s.
